Create java_config package.

Create a java configuration that does the same thing as xml_config.

Copy java_config to java_config_ext

Extend by adding AnotherHello, again, as per xml_config.

Copy AppConfig to AppConfigInterdependency.

Register Detail as a bean instead, and build as part of the AnotherBean creation, 
the Main class should remain unchanged.

Copy java_config.test to java_config_ext.test.

Add testAnotherBeansDetailDescriptionIsSunny test; this should run using either
AppConfig or AppConfigInterdependency.